<br>
<br>
<I> Monk nerf is just lame. Monks should be able to out dodge shit. WTF do you think a real martial artist does? </I><br>
<br>
well ask yourself, why be a warrior who gives up most of their offensive abilitye for higher ac items and supposed better dmg intake, yet monks take the dmg better plus they have a much better dps output? monks also better tanks then sks/pallies who also give up their offense for defense and give up duel weild for casting spells. try too look at the big picture not just the scope of one class. <br>
